{
  "video_id": "PYJ22-YYNW8",
  "title": "This is what makes employees happy at work | The Way We Work, a TED series",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 620.0,
      "end_time": 4649.0,
      "text": "We survey CEOs, police officers, truck drivers, cooks, engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4673.0,
      "end_time": 6698.0,
      "text": "If people are working, we&#39;ve surveyed them."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6721.0,
      "end_time": 8895.0,
      "text": "And what we know, in terms of their happiness:"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8919.0,
      "end_time": 10750.0,
      "text": "workers all want the same things."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10790.0,
      "end_time": 13175.0,
      "text": "[The Way We Work]"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15427.0,
      "end_time": 17792.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s three billion working people in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 17816.0,
      "end_time": 20705.0,
      "text": "And about 40 percent of them would say they&#39;re happy at work."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20729.0,
      "end_time": 24558.0,
      "text": "That means about 1.8 billion, or almost two billion people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24583.0,
      "end_time": 25956.0,
      "text": "are not happy at work."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25981.0,
      "end_time": 27184.0,
      "text": "What does that do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 27208.0,
      "end_time": 30433.0,
      "text": "both to those people and the organizations that they work in?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 30457.0,
      "end_time": 31885.0,
      "text": "Well, let&#39;s talk about money."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 31909.0,
      "end_time": 34745.0,
      "text": "Organizations that have a lot of happy employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 34769.0,
      "end_time": 36498.0,
      "text": "have three times the revenue growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 36523.0,
      "end_time": 38792.0,
      "text": "compared to organizations where that&#39;s not true."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 38816.0,
      "end_time": 41530.0,
      "text": "They outperform the stock market by a factor of three."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 41554.0,
      "end_time": 43435.0,
      "text": "And if you look at employee turnover,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 43459.0,
      "end_time": 47983.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s half that of organizations that have a lot of unhappy employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 48700.0,
      "end_time": 49183.0,
      "text": "The miracle thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 49207.0,
      "end_time": 51786.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t have to spend more money to make this happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 51810.0,
      "end_time": 54816.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not about ping-pong tables and massages and pet walking."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 54840.0,
      "end_time": 56780.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not about the perks."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 56102.0,
      "end_time": 58553.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s all about how they&#39;re treated by their leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 58578.0,
      "end_time": 60434.0,
      "text": "and by the people that they work with."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 60458.0,
      "end_time": 64450.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d like to share a few ideas that create happy employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 64474.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66940.0,
      "text": "Idea number one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 66118.0,
      "end_time": 68761.0,
      "text": "in organizations where employees are happy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 68785.0,
      "end_time": 70868.0,
      "text": "what you find is two things are present:"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 70892.0,
      "end_time": 72750.0,
      "text": "trust and respect."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 72432.0,
      "end_time": 73623.0,
      "text": "Leaders often say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 73647.0,
      "end_time": 75190.0,
      "text": "\"We trust our employees."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 75430.0,
      "end_time": 76535.0,
      "text": "We empower our employees.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 76559.0,
      "end_time": 78588.0,
      "text": "And then when an employee needs a laptop --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 78612.0,
      "end_time": 80330.0,
      "text": "and this is a true example --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 80580.0,
      "end_time": 82784.0,
      "text": "15 people have to approve that laptop."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 82808.0,
      "end_time": 85102.0,
      "text": "So for the employee, all the words are right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 85126.0,
      "end_time": 88963.0,
      "text": "but 15 levels of approval for a $1,500 laptop?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 88987.0,
      "end_time": 92217.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve actually spent more money than the laptop, on the approval."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 92242.0,
      "end_time": 95963.0,
      "text": "And the employee feels maybe they&#39;re really not trusted."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 95987.0,
      "end_time": 100398.0,
      "text": "So what can an organization do to have a high level of trust?"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 100422.0,
      "end_time": 103348.0,
      "text": "The first organization that comes to mind is Four Seasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 103372.0,
      "end_time": 106460.0,
      "text": "They have magnificent properties all around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 106700.0,
      "end_time": 107595.0,
      "text": "And their employees are told,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 107619.0,
      "end_time": 110697.0,
      "text": "\"Do whatever you think is right when servicing the customer.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 110721.0,
      "end_time": 115780.0,
      "text": "To hand that trust to your employees to do whatever they think is right"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 115102.0,
      "end_time": 116934.0,
      "text": "makes the employees feel great."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 116958.0,
      "end_time": 120217.0,
      "text": "And this is why they&#39;re known for delivering some of the best service"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 120241.0,
      "end_time": 121392.0,
      "text": "in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 121416.0,
      "end_time": 123956.0,
      "text": "Idea number two: fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 123980.0,
      "end_time": 127185.0,
      "text": "The thing that erodes trust in an organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 127209.0,
      "end_time": 128723.0,
      "text": "faster than anything else"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 128747.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131859.0,
      "text": "is when employees feel that they&#39;re being treated unfairly."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 131883.0,
      "end_time": 133737.0,
      "text": "Employees want to be treated the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 133761.0,
      "end_time": 136599.0,
      "text": "regardless of their rank or their tenure or their age"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 136623.0,
      "end_time": 138912.0,
      "text": "or their experience or their job category,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 138937.0,
      "end_time": 140388.0,
      "text": "compared to anyone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 140412.0,
      "end_time": 143477.0,
      "text": "When I think about great organizations who get fairness right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 143501.0,
      "end_time": 146126.0,
      "text": "the first organization that comes to mind is Salesforce."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 146150.0,
      "end_time": 148911.0,
      "text": "They found that men and women working in the same job"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 148935.0,
      "end_time": 150665.0,
      "text": "with the same level of proficiency"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 150689.0,
      "end_time": 152554.0,
      "text": "were making different amounts of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 152578.0,
      "end_time": 154935.0,
      "text": "So immediately, they calculated the difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 154959.0,
      "end_time": 158506.0,
      "text": "and they invested three million dollars to try and balance things out."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 159650.0,
      "end_time": 161246.0,
      "text": "Idea number three is listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 161617.0,
      "end_time": 165308.0,
      "text": "So, to be a listener who connects with all types of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 165332.0,
      "end_time": 167418.0,
      "text": "we have to unlearn a few things."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167443.0,
      "end_time": 171411.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve all been taught about active listening and eye contact --"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 171435.0,
      "end_time": 173165.0,
      "text": "an intense stare"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 173189.0,
      "end_time": 174911.0,
      "text": "and a compassionate look."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 174935.0,
      "end_time": 176114.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 176138.0,
      "end_time": 179200.0,
      "text": "Repeating what the person says -- that&#39;s not listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 179224.0,
      "end_time": 180433.0,
      "text": "Being humble"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 180457.0,
      "end_time": 183755.0,
      "text": "and always hunting and searching for the best idea possible --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 183779.0,
      "end_time": 185215.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s what listening is."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 185239.0,
      "end_time": 187875.0,
      "text": "And employees can feel whether you&#39;re doing that or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 187899.0,
      "end_time": 191860.0,
      "text": "They want to know, when they talk to you and share an idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 191110.0,
      "end_time": 193384.0,
      "text": "did you consider it when you made a decision?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 193408.0,
      "end_time": 197672.0,
      "text": "The one thing that everybody appreciates and wants when they&#39;re speaking"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 197697.0,
      "end_time": 201411.0,
      "text": "is to know that what they say matters so much"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 201435.0,
      "end_time": 203514.0,
      "text": "you might actually change your mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 203538.0,
      "end_time": 206500.0,
      "text": "Otherwise, what&#39;s the point of the conversation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 207533.0,
      "end_time": 209922.0,
      "text": "We all know the things we need to change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 209946.0,
      "end_time": 211978.0,
      "text": "the things that we need to do differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 212300.0,
      "end_time": 214629.0,
      "text": "The way you behave, the way you treat others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 214653.0,
      "end_time": 217935.0,
      "text": "the way you respond, the way you support,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 217959.0,
      "end_time": 220705.0,
      "text": "defines the work experience for everyone around you."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 220729.0,
      "end_time": 222769.0,
      "text": "Changing to be a better person --"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 222793.0,
      "end_time": 224816.0,
      "text": "the world is littered with those failures."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 224840.0,
      "end_time": 227746.0,
      "text": "But changing because there&#39;s something you believe in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 227770.0,
      "end_time": 229753.0,
      "text": "some purpose that you have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 229777.0,
      "end_time": 232338.0,
      "text": "where you&#39;re willing to risk almost everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 232362.0,
      "end_time": 234261.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s so important to you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 234285.0,
      "end_time": 235959.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the reason to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 235983.0,
      "end_time": 238381.0,
      "text": "If it&#39;s not, you should probably find a different place to work."
    }
  ]
}